- ğŸ¢ Safeguards **business continuity** and trust.  
- ğŸŒ Ensures **national security** (critical infrastructure, defense).  
- âš–ï¸ Helps meet **legal & regulatory compliance** (GDPR, HIPAA, IT Act).  

